ZH: 桃子是一种水果。
EN: Peach is a type of fruit.

ZH: 桃园里有很多成熟的桃子。
EN: There are many ripe peaches in the peach orchard.

ZH: 我喜欢吃桃子。
EN: I enjoy eating peaches.

ZH: 今年的桃子很甜。
EN: This year's peaches are very sweet.

ZH: 桃花盛开的时候，整个山谷都是粉色的。
EN: When peach blossoms bloom, the whole valley turns pink.

ZH: 我们一家人去桃园采摘桃子。
EN: My family went to the peach orchard to pick peaches.

ZH: 桃树的叶子在微风中摇曳。
EN: The leaves of the peach tree swayed in the breeze.

ZH: 你能帮我切一些桃子吗？
EN: Can you help me cut some peaches?

ZH: 桃子的种类很多，有白桃、黄桃等。
EN: There are many varieties of peaches, such as white peaches and yellow peaches.

ZH: 春天桃子的果实就会成熟。
EN: The peach fruit will ripen in the spring.

ZH: 桃树上结满了红红的桃子。
EN: The peach tree is covered with red peaches.

ZH: 秋天来临时，桃子就可以摘取了。
EN: When autumn arrives, it is time to pick the peaches.

ZH: 桃子含有丰富的维生素C。
EN: Peaches are rich in vitamin C.

ZH: 你吃过桃子冰激凌吗？
EN: Have you ever tried peach ice cream?

ZH: 桃叶的颜色比较淡。
EN: The color of peach leaves is relatively light.

ZH: 桃子的颜色是从绿色到红色再到橙色。
EN: The color of peaches ranges from green to red to orange.

ZH: 我们在桃园里摘了一篮子桃子。
EN: We picked a basket of peaches in the peach orchard.

ZH: 桃树长得很茂盛。
EN: The peach tree grows very vigorously.

ZH: 桃花绽放的时候，整个山坡都被染成了粉色。
EN: When the peach blossoms bloom, the whole hillside is dyed pink.

ZH: 桃子的价钱比较便宜。
EN: Peaches are relatively inexpensive.
